{"arkId":"cl010111556","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111556","modified ":"2026-02-10","title":"Plateau de d\u00e9jeuner \u0022\u00e0 rubans\u0022 \u00e0 fond \u0022beau bleu\u0022","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Plateau de d\u00e9jeuner \u0022\u00e0 rubans\u0022 \u00e0 fond \u0022beau bleu\u0022"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1777","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 620 - Djahangir Riahi, Vitrine 1A","room":"Salle 620, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1777,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"4e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"},{"label":"Leguay l\u0027A\u00een\u00e9, Etienne Henry","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1721","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1797","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Doreur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Pierre le Jeune, Jean Jacques","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1746","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1800","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Peintre sur c\u00e9ramique","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11918","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"plateau","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Ce plateau chantourn\u00e9 \u00e0 quatre lobes, destin\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027origine \u00e0 supporter un service \u00e0 th\u00e9  individuel, est entour\u00e9 de baguettes circulaires en relief, rehauss\u00e9es d\u0027or, qui se terminent \u00e0 chaque extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 par des rubans nou\u00e9s. Sous les baguettes, les bords du plateau sont festonn\u00e9s. L\u0027objet est en grande partie recouvert d\u0027un fond \u0022beau bleu\u0022. Au centre de la pi\u00e8ce, une r\u00e9serve quadrilob\u00e9e qui reprend la forme g\u00e9n\u00e9rale du plateau a \u00e9t\u00e9 am\u00e9nag\u00e9e. Cette r\u00e9serve, cern\u00e9e d\u0027un \u00e9pais filet d\u0027or, est orn\u00e9e d\u0027une belle nature morte dans le go\u00fbt n\u00e9oclassique. On distingue au fond de la composition un vase bleu \u00e0 l\u0027antique mont\u00e9 en bronze, entour\u00e9 de fruits en abondance, dispos\u00e9s sur un entablement de bois. Le fond bleu du plateau est rehauss\u00e9 d\u0027une dorure tr\u00e8s riche, form\u00e9e de motifs de trinceaux, de quadrillages et de guirlandes de feuillage.","inscriptions":"Marque de l\u0027atelier : \r ; Marques peintes en bleu : deux L entrelac\u00e9es ; lettre-date Z  (1777)\r ; Signature : \r ; Marque du peintre Jean-Jacques Pierre Jeune : p\u0027\r ; Marque en violet du doreur Etienne Henry Le Guay l\u0027A\u00een\u00e9 : LG","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,7","displayDimension":"5,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"39","displayDimension":"39 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"26","displayDimension":"26 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : porcelaine tendre\r\nTechnique : techniques c\u00e9ramique","placeOfCreation":"S\u00e8vres (Ile-de-Fr